    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>TOWING</title>
        <para>Do not tow vehicles equipped with Spicer transmission without first pulling the axles or disconnecting the
            drive shaft. Lubrication of the internal gear train is inadequate when the vehicle is towed.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
